00:00:24.119 --> 00:00:28.093
with respect to T when X is equal to nine.

00:00:28.093 --> 00:00:30.237
So, let's just make sure
we can understand this.

00:00:30.237 --> 00:00:34.214
So, they're telling us that
both X and Y are functions.

00:00:34.214 --> 00:00:36.553
Arguably they are both functions of T.

00:00:36.553 --> 00:00:38.097
